The list of materials

1x 5054 LED strip in either red,green or blue
    Optional Second strip for different color
1x AT-Tiny 85 microcontroller
2x TIP 120 BJT Transistor
2x 10k OHM resistor 
5x 2 Pin Screw Pluggable Terminal Block 5.08mm 
2x Voltage buck converter 
1x 100uF capacitor
1x 5A Fused cigarette lighter connector
1x 8ft of 16 gauge speaker wire
1x At-Tiny to USB chip OR standard arduino uno board